I need to collaborate with other robots to form an equilateral triangle with a side length of 100 and a center at (150, 100). One robot must be on the edge but not at a vertex. First, I need to sense my current position to determine my role in the formation.

```
[
  { "cmd": "sense" }
]
```

I have waited for 10 seconds and sensed my position again, which is (125.0, 56.7) and my direction is 355.5 degrees. I am at vertex 3. I will now go to idle mode.

```
[
  { "cmd": "idle" }
]
```

Since I have not received any response from trial7_robot4, I assume it is still trying to move. I will just go to idle since I have done my part.

```
[
  { "cmd": "idle" }
]
```
